Dialogue: 0,0:00:18.35,0:00:24.30,Default,op,0,0,0,,Under the skies that are still unknown to me
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.30,0:00:28.40,Default,op,0,0,0,,I know, you're doing just the same -
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.40,0:00:29.98,Default,op,0,0,0,,Dreaming
Dialogue: 0,0:00:29.98,0:00:35.24,Default,op,0,0,0,,Just a small glow\NFrom those great days
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.24,0:00:38.12,Default,op,0,0,0,,Is what dragging you along
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.12,0:00:41.87,Default,op,0,0,0,,Giving you faith and some comfort
Dialogue: 0,0:00:41.87,0:00:45.79,Default,op,0,0,0,,Under the sun that scorches badly
Dialogue: 0,0:00:48.00,0:00:52.17,Default,op,0,0,0,,I only want to see your guise
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.17,0:00:53.91,Default,op,0,0,0,,But instead...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.91,0:00:59.18,Default,op,0,0,0,,I only watch \NWith tears on my face
Dialogue: 0,0:00:59.18,0:01:04.77,Default,op,0,0,0,,As you slowly disappear in this noon haze
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.77,0:01:07.76,Default,op,0,0,0,,We're alone \NWe're alone
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.76,0:01:11.31,Default,op,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,1000)}Walking this world on our own
Dialogue: 1,0:01:10.36,0:01:16.53,Default,op,0,0,0,,{\fade(1000,0)}Looking for each other since long ago
Dialogue: 0,0:01:16.53,0:01:22.49,Default,op,0,0,0,,In the end, in the end, \NAfter the day we finally meet
Dialogue: 0,0:01:22.49,0:01:27.00,Default,op,0,0,0,,{\b1\bord1\blur1\t(2100,2200,\shad3\blur3\c&HABADD8&)}We won't ever have to say "Goodbye"
Comment: 0,0:01:33.06,0:01:37.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{OP END}
Dialogue: 0,0:01:52.21,0:01:53.18,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:53.59,0:01:56.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Your participation in Tokyo Cup in two weeks is confirmed.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:57.34,0:02:01.53,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(0,2000)}Just what you need to get in shape for the autumn season.
Dialogue: 1,0:01:59.83,0:02:05.10,Default,,0,0,0,,{\fade(2000,0)}We only have two weeks \Nso get used to the intense schedule starting tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:05.87,0:02:08.10,Default,,0,0,0,,Was everything alright in the temple?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:10.21,0:02:12.61,Default,,0,0,0,,Which means Todo too...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:13.32,0:02:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I dismissed him from the temple so he could prepare{ for the flight}. \NHe will enter America's circuit at 3000th position. {Might as well be something like "He will need $3000 to enter American circuit." I'm sorta lost}
Dialogue: 0,0:02:25.12,0:02:28.13,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo's departure date has finally been fixed...
Dialogue: 0,0:02:28.13,0:02:30.65,Default,,0,0,0,,Well, it's the day after tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:30.65,0:02:34.63,Default,,0,0,0,,So I thought we could arrange \Nsome modest kind of seeing-off party.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:34.63,0:02:37.63,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. Oka told me she approves it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:37.63,0:02:41.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Right. Yes. Right. Got it.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:43.14,0:02:45.64,Default,,0,0,0,,Indeed, Todo chose an outstanding path.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:46.77,0:02:51.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Becoming a pro means suffering \Nhuge travel, living, and entry fee expenses.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:51.30,0:02:55.34,Default,,0,0,0,,One finds a reliable sponsor first \Nto cover most of those expenses for him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:55.34,0:02:59.07,Default,,0,0,0,,However, all the major sponsors were rejected by him.
Dialogue: 0,0:02:59.07,0:03:03.31,Default,,0,0,0,,As a winner of Japan's Open, \Nwith a recommendation from our Tennis Association,
Dialogue: 0,0:03:03.31,0:03:07.22,Default,,0,0,0,,he could get into many American tournaments \Nwithout having to qualify.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.22,0:03:12.82,Default,,0,0,0,,But he never asked for a recommendation. \NHe is trying to start his journey from a true Zero.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.82,0:03:15.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Why do you think he does that, Reika?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:15.32,0:03:18.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Like a lunatic monk, \Nhe pushes himself to the limit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.09,0:03:21.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Why in the world is he so obsessed \Nwith alienating his country?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:21.82,0:03:27.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Perhaps, somebody convinced him once \Nto follow his own way with a wholehearted dedication.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:27.04,0:03:29.45,Default,,0,0,0,,What? Who?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:38.88,0:03:43.89,Default,,0,0,100,,{\bord4\blur15\3c&HE3C4A2&\t(0,1100,\bord0.11\blur0.5\3c&H945431&)\c&HF7EEF0&\fnGabriola\fs48\frz359.6\an8\fscx167\fscy157}Episode 3
Dialogue: 0,0:04:00.07,0:04:01.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka! Hiromi!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:02.97,0:04:04.28,Default,,0,0,0,,Ms. Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:04:03.88,0:04:04.74,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}This way.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:04:04.74,0:04:05.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:08.56,0:04:10.37,Default,,0,0,0,,We need to get to the top floor{ of this building}.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:17.11,0:04:19.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Summer is almost over.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:20.89,0:04:21.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.97,0:04:25.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I wonder if Todo will be home by winter.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:46.43,0:04:48.93,Default,,0,0,0,,Our obnoxious friend is leaving Japan all alone.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:49.89,0:04:52.92,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not like going abroad is something special these days.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:53.33,0:04:56.89,Default,,0,0,0,,But for now we better get used \Nto no longer seeing each other daily.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:58.59,0:05:02.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Therefore, tonight, we send Todo off appropriately. \NQuietly and collectedly.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:02.56,0:05:07.90,Default,,0,0,0,,So to make sure you fare well, I want to say: \Nneither the one sent off, nor those who send him off will have any regrets.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:07.90,0:05:09.57,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why we met here tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:09.57,0:05:14.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo, to whatever is ahead,\Nwe raise this 63rd vintage Château Burgundy. {Might as well be 63 years old, but that'd be tenfold as expensive}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:16.23,0:05:17.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Cheers!
Dialogue: 0,0:05:17.21,0:05:18.11,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cheers!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.11,0:05:19.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you...
Dialogue: 0,0:05:39.83,0:05:41.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Be in touch at least once a week.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:43.82,0:05:46.82,Default,,0,0,0,,Come on, Ozaki.\NTodo is not some child.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:46.82,0:05:48.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Whether the times are easy,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:48.49,0:05:50.50,Default,,0,0,0,,whether they are rough, \Neither way,
Dialogue: 0,0:05:50.51,0:05:54.50,Default,,0,0,0,,anyone you see here - \Nmake sure to stay in touch with any of us here.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:54.50,0:05:59.35,Default,,0,0,0,,Not because we fear you will feel lonely, \Nbut because we will be uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.35,0:06:02.52,Default,,0,0,0,,As long as you don't give us any response,\Nwe will be uneasy.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:06.36,0:06:08.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I heard you, Ozaki.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:15.03,0:06:20.54,Default,,0,0,0,,In conclusion, while you will be there, \Nyou shouldn't be trying to impersonate Mr. Munakata.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:20.54,0:06:26.05,Default,,0,0,0,,You are you only. And not Munakata Jin. \NYou have always been Todo Takayuki. Let it remain that way.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:26.05,0:06:27.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Whichever the place and time.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:29.92,0:06:32.07,Default,,0,0,0,,Mr. Munakata has died.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:33.10,0:06:34.02,Default,,0,0,0,,He did not die.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:34.68,0:06:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He died!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:36.58,0:06:37.75,Default,,0,0,0,,He didn't die!
Dialogue: 0,0:06:40.90,0:06:41.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Fool.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.25,0:06:48.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Good luck, in absence of a better word.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:54.99,0:06:58.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No one managed to dissuade you after all.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.75,0:07:01.88,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.56,0:07:04.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you, Madame Butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.86,0:07:06.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Oka.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.51,0:07:10.88,Default,,0,0,0,,You have not been very voluble tonight.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.49,0:07:13.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't you and Todo have a lot to say to each other?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:14.76,0:07:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,No. Actually... Actually, I don't have anything...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:16.97,0:07:20.21,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}You do, you do, you do. You surely do. Now, Todo. She's listening.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.24,0:07:23.44,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:24.84,0:07:30.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo remains loyal to the righteous cause. \NHe carries on doing what he has made his mind to.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:30.03,0:07:35.75,Default,,0,0,0,,And since Todo chose this \NI will think of it as a righteous cause as well.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.25,0:07:39.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't give up, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:53.40,0:07:55.60,Default,,0,0,0,,Now, let's get a bit more boozed, Todo.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.92,0:08:07.43,Default,,0,0,0,,You applied for the coming Autumn Tokyo Cup, \Ndidn't you, Oka?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.42,0:08:10.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes. I did.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:10.45,0:08:13.45,Default,,0,0,0,,I participate in entries too. \NLet's do our best together.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.82,0:08:14.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:16.43,0:08:17.76,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Cheers!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.49,0:08:38.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Crap! I forgot to ask the plane departure time tomorrow!
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.97,0:08:43.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey Todo, sure you don't feel like calling your beloved one?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:44.96,0:08:47.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Tonight is your last chance to see each other.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:48.17,0:08:50.11,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't have any "beloved ones."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:50.86,0:08:53.47,Default,,0,0,0,,At 21 it's essential to have one or two.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:53.47,0:08:58.21,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo's love belongs to tennis. \NSuch is Munakata Jin ghost's precept.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:58.21,0:08:59.23,Default,,0,0,0,,You can't be sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:59.23,0:09:01.54,Default,,0,0,0,,Good God, you really need to mature, man!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:01.54,0:09:04.65,Default,,0,0,0,,You say that because you have like 5 to 6 ex-lovers yourself?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:04.65,0:09:05.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Ten of them!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.37,0:09:08.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Is something wrong with my looks? \NI don't have a single one.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:29.82,0:09:31.53,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Todo?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:33.03,0:09:35.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Well then.\NShall we be on our ways.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.03,0:09:44.33,Default,,0,0,0,,See you, Todo. Make sure your luggage is packed and ready \Nwhen I pick you up tomorrow.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.33,0:09:45.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:45.79,0:09:46.50,Default,,0,0,0,,See ya!
Dialogue: 0,0:09:57.62,0:10:01.93,Default,,0,0,0,,I wanted to talk to Oka just a little bit more.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:11.34,0:10:16.74,Default,,0,0,0,,He will, surely!\NTodo will surely find a way to let me know.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:40.91,0:10:43.41,Default,,0,0,0,,It's too late. \NShe is sleeping already.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:45.67,0:10:47.67,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello? Hello!
Dialogue: 0,0:10:50.17,0:10:54.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Hello, is that you, Todo? \NPlease tell me this one more little thing.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:54.37,0:11:01.06,Default,,0,0,0,,What time does you plane take off tomorrow?\NJust once more, even for a moment, I want to see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:43.36,0:11:47.88,Default,,0,0,0,,I don't want to be seen a capricious child.\NI don't want to see myself a capricious child.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:49.31,0:11:51.84,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka Hiromi. 19 years old.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:51.84,0:11:58.87,Default,,0,0,0,,Falling in love is nothing extraordinary. And being thrilled about meeting someone is nothing extraordinary! Still...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:58.87,0:12:01.86,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, I'm not sure if it's love that is driving me now.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:04.39,0:12:10.39,Default,,0,0,0,,Everyone says the person I love is making a mistake. \NThat he should not try to climb further. That he should not be naive.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.63,0:12:14.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I myself have stopped halfway in every of my undertakings.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.77,0:12:19.28,Default,,0,0,0,,There is probably not a single thing I can do \Nto help Todo right now. {There's probably not a single thing in me that could be wholesome for Todo.}
Dialogue: 0,0:12:20.67,0:12:21.78,Default,,0,0,0,,Besides...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:22.40,0:12:25.39,Default,,0,0,0,,I would probably lack courage for it...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:42.95,0:12:46.41,Default,,0,0,0,,Those are the flowers \NI gave to Todo yesterday!
Dialogue: 0,0:12:51.93,0:12:55.94,Default,,0,0,20,,{\an8\b0\fnVerdana}Dear Oka, \Nat 20:15 I am departing from Narita \NFlight 522\NT.T
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.98,0:13:04.15,Default,,0,0,0,,To Oka: \Nat 20:15 I depart from Narita. Flight 522.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:06.15,0:13:07.77,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm ready!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:07.77,0:13:08.58,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:34.18,0:13:36.49,Default,,0,0,0,,Sorry. We made you wait.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:36.49,0:13:41.25,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's you who should excuse me. \NIt's been some time since I last fought an actual match.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.25,0:13:46.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka! You will play a 3-set match with Ryuzaki! \NThis training game will show you what to hone next!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:46.25,0:13:48.72,Default,,0,0,0,,So unexpectedly. Do I have enough time?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:48.72,0:13:50.26,Default,,0,0,0,,Get to the baseline!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:50.26,0:13:53.73,Default,,0,0,0,,To get there by 20:15, \NI have to leave the court no later than at 5!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.73,0:13:55.14,Default,,0,0,0,,No slacking off!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:55.14,0:13:56.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.82,0:14:04.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi, I'll keep my game plain, but rough!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:04.79,0:14:07.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay! I'm ready when you are!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.55,0:14:10.85,Default,,0,0,0,,And then practice?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:11.55,0:14:14.05,Default,,0,0,0,,Somehow Hiromi has less and less free time. {/ Hiromi has not been socializing well lately.}
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.18,0:14:16.18,Default,,0,0,0,,You think so?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:16.18,0:14:17.72,Default,,0,0,0,,When does your practice end?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:17.72,0:14:19.30,Default,,0,0,0,,Let me think... At 5 PM.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.30,0:14:23.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Then, let's go see a movie after that! \NI'll meet you by the "Club."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:23.99,0:14:25.34,Default,,0,0,0,,Actually...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:25.34,0:14:27.34,Default,,0,0,0,,What now? \NYou can't again?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.99,0:14:30.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I am enlisted for the Autumn Tokyo Cup...
Dialogue: 0,0:14:30.73,0:14:33.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Coach Katsura's appointment? \NStrategy meeting?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:34.29,0:14:35.28,Default,,0,0,0,,You could say that.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:35.29,0:14:42.29,Default,,0,0,0,,Figures. He always makes you go full steam ahead.\NHow can he not, since you're nothing like a usual player of my sort?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:42.29,0:14:44.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Of course! Hiromi is fine with it!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.23,0:14:45.74,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.51,0:14:47.75,Default,,0,0,0,,Nevermind.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:47.75,0:14:51.03,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry I couldn't go to the sea.\NDid something happen there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:51.03,0:14:53.51,Default,,0,0,0,,No, there was nothing.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:53.51,0:14:57.56,Default,,0,0,0,,Maki, cheer up! \NI'm carving out a time to hang out with you soon. A whole day!
Dialogue: 0,0:14:58.37,0:15:01.08,Default,,0,0,0,,But today, sorry. I can't come along.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:01.08,0:15:03.73,Default,,0,0,0,,I should have carried on playing tennis too.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:22.94,0:15:27.46,Default,,0,0,0,,Game for Ryuzaki! Game count: 6-1!\NSet count: 1-0!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.64,0:15:32.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Hiromi.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:32.68,0:15:33.23,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.23,0:15:36.23,Default,,0,0,0,,When you rush in to the ball, \Nyou make half a step less than usual.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.47,0:15:40.71,Default,,0,0,0,,You keep missing my forehands \Neven though I'm still out of shape.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:40.71,0:15:41.90,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sorry!
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.78,0:15:50.24,Default,,0,0,0,,It's not really about going pro or not.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:50.24,0:15:53.72,Default,,0,0,0,,As well as it's not really about standing on top of the world.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.72,0:16:00.56,Default,,0,0,0,,But when my friend puts on full power with no second thoughts, \Nit is a mighty incentive for me to start something great myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.56,0:16:04.23,Default,,0,0,0,,These days, there are no other guys that daring, \Nnot even myself.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.26,0:16:10.09,Default,,0,0,0,,Among common folk, devoting oneself to something wholly{/ enthusiastically} \Nis seen as an outre{/ untoward / bizarre} way to embarrassment{/ chagrin}.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:10.09,0:16:14.67,Default,,0,0,0,,The best those people can do is to flock around{/ follow the example of those who surround them to root enthusiastically for the} one \Nwho is considered favorite.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:14.67,0:16:18.66,Default,,0,0,0,,Such rabble lives just to yell "Loser!" to one another \Nand fress on every entr'acte,
Dialogue: 0,0:16:19.27,0:16:21.16,Default,,0,0,0,,with little repentance afterwards.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:21.16,0:16:23.00,Default,,0,0,0,,Please focus on the road. {/ don't get us plunged into the sea. — this one is more literal}
Dialogue: 0,0:16:23.67,0:16:28.68,Default,,0,0,0,,Had I not known a man named Munakata Jin, \NI'd never get here.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:38.29,0:16:41.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Out! The second set score is 5-1! \NRyuzaki lead!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:41.79,0:16:45.83,Default,,0,0,0,,This is bad! If I go on giving away every game with an out, \NI'll lose the match!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:45.83,0:16:49.75,Default,,0,0,0,,However, I could leave this court once the match is over!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:49.75,0:16:53.76,Default,,0,0,0,,The flight is at 20:15. \NIf I go now, I can still get there on time!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:53.76,0:16:56.78,Default,,0,0,0,,I may at least be able to see Todo in the lounge!
Dialogue: 0,0:16:56.78,0:16:59.76,Default,,0,0,0,,Oka! Quit dilly-dallying!{WHAT THE FUCK THIS IS INAUDIBLE}\NIt's your service!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:01.22,0:17:04.29,Default,,0,0,0,,That's why I must do my best either way.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:04.29,0:17:06.29,Default,,0,0,0,,The opponent is Madame Butterfly.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:06.29,0:17:09.02,Default,,0,0,0,,I cannot afford to lose intentionally!
Dialogue: 0,0:17:27.33,0:17:29.14,Default,,0,0,0,,Need your help. This is heavy.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:28.73,0:17:29.55,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Gotcha!{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:34.80,0:17:37.32,Default,,0,0,0,,Leaving for New York with flight 522?
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.32,0:17:37.82,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Yes.{\i0}
Dialogue: 0,0:17:37.82,0:17:39.12,Default,,0,0,0,,Your luggage, please.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:41.11,0:17:44.93,Default,,0,0,0,,OK! There's still plenty of time until the boarding. \NLet's drink and talk it away.
Dialogue: 0,0:17:45.60,0:17:46.20,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:21.37,0:18:22.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Game!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:22.70,0:18:27.31,Default,,0,0,0,,Game count: 7-5!\NSet count: 2-0! Winner - Ryuzaki!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:31.71,0:18:33.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Thank you so much!
Dialogue: 0,0:18:34.17,0:18:39.18,Default,,0,0,0,,More than to win, I was happy to see Hiromi fight \Njust as vigorously in the second half after such a long time.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:40.31,0:18:44.64,Default,,0,0,0,,You started the second set losing 5 to 1.\NBut pulled it to 7-5 eventually. Not bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:45.91,0:18:46.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:46.81,0:18:49.81,Default,,0,0,0,,Alright, enough for today! \NDismissed, everyone.
Dialogue: 0,0:18:49.81,0:18:50.90,Default,,0,0,0,,If you excuse me!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:00.02,0:19:01.43,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I make it in time?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:01.99,0:19:03.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Will I not?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:06.64,0:19:07.96,Default,,0,0,0,,Goddammit!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:13.15,0:19:19.03,Default,,0,0,0,,Flight 522 to New York passengers \Nmay now begin their boarding.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:22.95,0:19:25.06,Default,,0,0,0,,Madame, at what time do you have the flight?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:25.06,0:19:26.23,Default,,0,0,0,,20:15!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:27.15,0:19:28.73,Default,,0,0,0,,That's a bummer...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:31.12,0:19:32.53,Default,,0,0,0,,Going to your boyfriend?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:33.69,0:19:35.67,Default,,0,0,0,,I mean, seeing him off?
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.24,0:19:36.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Yes...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:36.77,0:19:42.24,Default,,0,0,0,,What a spicy story! You fell in love with a foreigner, \Nbut now he has to leave. My, how spicy it is...
Dialogue: 0,0:19:42.97,0:19:45.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Having to follow a foreigner sure is an ordeal!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:49.27,0:19:50.15,Default,,0,0,0,,My bad.
Dialogue: 0,0:19:50.71,0:19:52.72,Default,,0,0,0,,Don't worry, I'll get you there in time!
Dialogue: 0,0:19:56.66,0:20:02.92,Default,,0,0,0,,Passengers of the plane 522 to New York, \Nleaving at 20:15, are requested to proceed to the board.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:02.92,0:20:06.45,Default,,0,0,0,,The 63rd gate is ready to accept you.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:05.87,0:20:08.52,Default,,0,0,0,,{\i1}Hey, Todo. About time you start going.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:08.52,0:20:12.02,Default,,0,0,0,,Just a bit more...\NThere's still some coffee left.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:12.02,0:20:15.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Hey, Todo!\NWhat's with that sudden dither?
Dialogue: 0,0:20:17.49,0:20:19.01,Default,,0,0,0,,No, it's nothing...
Dialogue: 0,0:20:28.60,0:20:29.37,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:29.88,0:20:31.04,Default,,0,0,0,,Wait, Chiba.
Dialogue: 0,0:20:45.30,0:20:48.62,Default,,0,0,0,,I have been playing \Na practice match with Madame Butterfly!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:48.62,0:20:53.17,Default,,0,0,0,,6-1 and 7-5 - I lost both sets. \NBut this time I almost felt like I'm winning!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:53.17,0:20:56.77,Default,,0,0,0,,Just one step... No. \NI was just half a step away!
Dialogue: 0,0:20:58.55,0:21:02.98,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm sure you can do it. \NYou can certainly make this one or even two steps more.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:08.33,0:21:09.52,Default,,0,0,0,,Goodbye...
Dialogue: 0,0:21:10.29,0:21:11.89,Default,,0,0,0,,Never say goodbye.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:12.89,0:21:13.80,Default,,0,0,0,,Okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:13.80,0:21:14.98,Default,,0,0,0,,Take care.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:14.98,0:21:16.52,Default,,0,0,0,,You too, Todo.
Dialogue: 0,0:21:49.36,0:21:54.48,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo, I love you too.
Comment: 0,0:22:10.29,0:22:13.62,Default,,0,0,0,,{ED START}
Dialogue: 0,0:22:15.47,0:22:21.22,Default,ed,0,0,0,,There is one song I cannot ever forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:21.22,0:22:26.85,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Still, there's a face I'm willing to forget
Dialogue: 0,0:22:26.85,0:22:29.81,Default,ed,0,0,0,,With her feelings mixed up,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:29.81,0:22:32.69,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Alice got completely lost
Dialogue: 0,0:22:32.69,0:22:37.88,Default,ed,0,0,0,,The midst of summer \NBrought her into one tricky love maze
Dialogue: 0,0:22:39.20,0:22:44.79,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I want you to hug tightly\NAnd never let go of me,
Dialogue: 0,0:22:44.79,0:22:50.17,Default,ed,0,0,0,,One scared and timid tiny girl
Dialogue: 0,0:22:50.17,0:22:57.05,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I quite remember our very first kiss \NAnd the beginning of all of this
Dialogue: 0,0:22:57.63,0:23:03.47,Default,ed,0,0,0,,While birds were singing for us...
Dialogue: 0,0:23:06.54,0:23:12.66,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I'll take a car and take a lonely trip
Dialogue: 0,0:23:12.66,0:23:17.86,Default,ed,0,0,0,,I know it'll bring me \NTo the seashore
Dialogue: 0,0:23:17.86,0:23:20.91,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Where only the the sun,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:20.91,0:23:23.95,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Dazzlingly bright,
Dialogue: 0,0:23:23.95,0:23:29.48,Default,ed,0,0,0,,Could witness my long-awaited happiness
Dialogue: 0,0:23:36.16,0:23:37.38,Default,,0,0,0,,I'm Aikawa Maki.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:38.46,0:23:41.94,Default,,0,0,0,,Todo has left for New York\Nand Hiromi feels very lonely.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:42.44,0:23:43.70,Default,,0,0,0,,Fight, alright? Fight!
Dialogue: 0,0:23:44.28,0:23:47.35,Default,,0,0,0,,The Tokyo Cup match is coming at us imminently.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:48.05,0:23:50.25,Default,,0,0,0,,Though Todo is away, he'll surely do his best.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:51.12,0:23:54.45,Default,,0,0,0,,Still, when the game day comes,\NHiromi is still acting weird.
Dialogue: 0,0:23:54.63,0:23:57.87,Default,,0,0,0,,What's the matter, Hiromi?\NHas something happened to Todo?
Dialogue: 0,0:23:58.66,0:24:01.79,Default,,0,0,0,,Coming soon: "I want to see you, Todo..."
